high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward. Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the sink.
Turn around completely and face the left.
Place the spoon on the counter to the right of you.
Turn to the right and walk to the island.
Pick up the spoon off the island.
Turn around and walk to the counter.
Place the spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and head to the end of the green table that is on the right then turn left and go to the sink
Take the spoon out of the sink
Turn around and face the stove
Put the spoon on the counter near the tomato
Turn right and go to the table
Pick up the spoon from the table
Turn around and go towards the sink then turn right
Stand the spoon in its end next to the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons on the counter

high_descs: Move right then left towards the kitchen sink
Pick up the spoon inside of the sink in the front right of the sink
Carry the spoon towards the green counter to the right of the sink
Place the spoon on top of the counter to the right of the sink
Turn around and move straight to the green table top
Pick up the spoon on the table top behind the pump bottle
Carry the spoon over to the right side of the sink
Place the spoon vertically on top of the other spoon handle sitting on the counter top
anns.task_desc: Move two spoons to the counter top
